Introduction
This Privacy Policy describes how the extension collects, uses, and protects information gathered through our internal Chrome extension ("the Extension"). The Extension is designed exclusively for use by employees of Vodafone Egypt on company portals. It captures specific actions of employees to enhance productivity, improve system performance, and ensure compliance with company policies. This extension is used only locally within our company network.

Information We Collect:
Types of Data Collected

User Actions:
Clicks, username, PC name and navigation within company portals.

Technical Information:
Browser type and version.
Operating system.
IP addresses and device identifiers used within the company network.

Purpose of Data Collection
Productivity Analysis: To understand and enhance employee productivity.
System Performance: To identify and resolve technical issues on company portals.
Compliance: To ensure adherence to company policies and regulatory requirements.

How We Use the Information

Data Analysis:
Aggregating and analyzing data to improve user experience on company portals.
Identifying trends and patterns to optimize workflows and system performance.

Security and Compliance:
Monitoring compliance with company policies.
Detecting and preventing unauthorized activities.

Data Security
We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect the data collected through the Extension against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. Access to collected data is restricted to authorized personnel only and is protected by strong authentication mechanisms.

Data Sharing and Disclosure
Internal Use: Data collected by the Extension is used solely within Vodafone Egypt and is not shared with external parties.
Legal Compliance: We may disclose data if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities.

Data Retention
Data collected by the Extension will be retained only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. Once the data is no longer needed, it will be securely deleted or anonymized.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. Employees will be notified of any significant changes.
